{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"fields":{"description":"## Description\nAdd a `[code_health]` config SECTION (schema + defaults + override parsing) so each client declares scan roots, per-language tool selection, size policy, and an enable flag. SCOPE IS SCHEMA-ONLY — this ticket does not change any metric runtime behavior and does not remove any hardcode; consuming the config + the Unavailable-on-unconfigured behavior land in migration 0734.\n\n## Review-driven corrections\n- Removed the \"replaces the hardcoded src/rebar / cap file\" and \"absent config -> code_health Unavailable\" claims: those hardcodes live in git_metrics.py and their removal + runtime fallback are 0734s job. This ticket only DEFINES the typed keys.\n- Name concrete keys/types in `_config_schema.py` dataclass.\n- Adding a section changes the pinned surface guard `tests/golden/config_surface.json` (checked by tests/unit/test_config_surface_golden.py) — regenerate + review it.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- [ ] `[code_health]` dataclass in `_config_schema.py` with concrete keys: `enabled: bool=False`, `scan_roots: list[str]`, `analyzers: dict[str,str]` (lang->tool), `size_cap: int|None`, `size_near_fraction: float`.\n- [ ] Defaults documented; `rebar -c code_health.<key>=<val>` overrides parse via the existing path; section re-exported through config.py.\n- [ ] `tests/golden/config_surface.json` regenerated to include the section; golden test green.\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] Unit: default load, `-c` override parse, missing-section default. Golden surface test passes.\n\n## Dependencies: 3b30 (interface). Recorded edge: depends_on 3b30.\n## Files likely touched: src/rebar/_config_schema.py, src/rebar/config.py, tests/golden/config_surface.json, tests/unit/test_code_health_config.py (new)\n## Estimated scope: M"}},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"EDIT","timestamp":1784523331943027001,"uuid":"c0d42cfb-f8dc-4e12-8607-c036fc42555e"}